data.description: Welcome to this meticulously maintained and tastefully refreshed Spacious Family Home! This charming two-story residence features 4 bedrooms and 3.5 baths, with a delightful front porch and swing for relaxation. Step inside to discover a beautifully updated interior, where the home has been freshly painted, creating a bright and inviting atmosphere throughout. You'll find dual master suites - one upstairs and one downstairs, along with two guest bedrooms. The upstairs guest bathroom is a treat with a jacuzzi tub, perfect for relaxation. The home also boasts a formal dining room for elegant gatherings, and a large eat-in kitchen with a farmhouse sink and walk-in pantry. Cozy up by the wood-burning fireplace in the family room and enjoy the screened porch. Step into the fenced backyard, offering a shed for storage and a dog run area. This family home is conveniently located near the YMCA park, providing easy access to recreational facilities, sports fields, playgrounds, and fitness centers. Tucked away in Sebring, this home offers proximity to amenities. Don't miss out - schedule a showing today!
